## Third-Party Notices

### MaxMind GeoLite2

This product includes GeoLite2 data created by MaxMind, available from
https://www.maxmind.com. The GeoLite2 database is licensed under the
Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International License (CC BY-SA 4.0).
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

### Natural Earth

Geographic border data is derived from Natural Earth, a public domain map dataset
available from https://www.naturalearthdata.com. Natural Earth data is in the
public domain and free for use in any manner without restriction.

